isional-driving-licence\" title=\"provisional driving licence\">provisional driving licence</a> entitlement and then pass a tractor or specialist vehicle driving test to get your full licence.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You don’t need a licence to drive a tractor or specialist vehicle <strong>off the public road</strong> but there are <a href=\"/learning-to-drive-a-tractor-or-specialist-vehicle/age-limits\" title=\"age limits\">age limits</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You also don’t need a licence to operate pedestrian-controlled mowing machines, but you must be at least 16.</p>\n\n<h2>Road rollers and tracked vehicles</h2>\n\n<p>As well as the right provisional entitlement you’ll also need to hold a full car licence (category B) before you can drive:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>road rollers</li>\n  <li>tracked vehicles</li>\n</ul>\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/learning-to-drive-a-tractor-or-specialist-vehicle/age-limits","slug":"age-limits","order":2,"title":"Age limits","body":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Category</th>\n      <th>Description</th>\n      <th>Minimum age</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>B1</td>\n      <td>Motor tricycles, quadricycles and 3 or 4-wheeled vehicles with an unladen weight no more than 550 kg</td>\n      <td>17*</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>F</td>\n      <td>Agricultural tractors</td>\n      <td>16/17**</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>G</td>\n      <td>Road rollers</td>\n      <td>21***</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>H</td>\n      <td>Tracked vehicles</td>\n      <td>17/21†</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>K</td>\n      <td>Mowing machine or pedestrian-controlled vehicle</td>\n      <td>16</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>*16 if you&rsquo;re currently getting Disability Living Allowance at the higher rate (mobility component).</p>\n\n<p>**If you’re 16 you can only drive tractors less than 2.45 metres wide and tow trailers less than 2.45 metres wi